{"tid":2155761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金融時報：港新聞自由已死","createTime":"2020-08-14T04:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T04:09:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9fab500fe9f7b6292d5cf12547276cdd60efc7c","tid":2155761,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:09:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/67O6MZO6MBE6VHUBLKJE6JFU7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2F67O6MZO6MBE6VHUBLKJE6JFU7Y%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=14fd6e47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2F67O6MZO6MBE6VHUBLKJE6JFU7Y%2F&h=5470e2ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/67O6MZO6MBE6VHUBLKJE6JFU7Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n金融時報：港新聞自由已死<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》社論指警方國安處高調拘捕黎智英並大舉搜查《蘋果日報》編採部，兩件事象徵香港新聞自由已死，「北京會克制引用國安法、維持一國兩制」的幻想亦破滅，黎不會是國安法下唯一被捕傳媒人，工會、出版、宗教和人權組織亦受威脅；。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：獲釋後Twitter直播  黎智英：手銬不能侮辱我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dwqIahBPYRO646c0YBlLqNhhw3c=/1239x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D7UNMUW4CZDQNAUA4VPENNDEDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdwqIahBPYRO646c0YBlLqNhhw3c%3D%2F1239x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD7UNMUW4CZDQNAUA4VPENNDEDU.jpg&h=ead574b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《金融時報》社論指港府打壓新聞自由，終會令香港走向死亡。"}]}